summary:
Through my previous experience as a Consultant in different sectors of the Economy, such as Transport, Automotive and Electrical industries, I improved to perfection my organizational effectiveness, as well as I developed  a specific approach to each customer, as a result to be increased over all customers satisfaction.

I have a master degree from the Technical University of Varna, Bulgaria.

I am searching new possibilities, in order to improve professionally and to contribute to the success of the company and its clients.
I can be reached at d.tsenovabg@gmail.com.
